reviews.review_text: Nice! excellent quality, and a ferocious Space>Jam>Other One!  Great Shakedown to open show, too.

I like this one... ...alot!

I streamed this on 4-16-21; the first set in the morning, and the second set in the evening, after work.  Lots of good stuff here~
